org.apache.poi.hdgf.chunks

Class ChunkFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.poi.hdgf.chunks.ChunkFactory

  • public final class ChunkFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    Factor class to create the appropriate chunks, which needs the version of the file to process the chunk header and trailer areas. Makes use of chunks_parse_cmds.tbl from vsdump to be able to process the chunk value area(Factor类来创建适当的块，这需要文件的版本来处理块头和尾部区域。使用vsdump中的chunks_parse_cmds.tBL能够处理块值区域)
